Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.92,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.70,0:00:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.71,0:00:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.19,0:01:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二話重力的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真實的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與美麗同時兼具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人類的希望!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是神話般的景象啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思議了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋艦隊已進入備戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統，請下達最後的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速素粒子砲，準備射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備射擊!\N加速素粒子砲展開射角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位角4600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位角4600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速粒子射線壓100
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位注意\N重力子能量的臨界值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.17,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦達到臨界值\N合神會被強制解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼的話\N我們將失去一切反擊之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的命運亦將自此畫上休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到外星異種這麼頑強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜、愛娜\N有沒有嚇壞了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢!\N人...人家有一點點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下模擬訓練的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麼的話\N我會幫妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰在操控?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是...綾香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在戰鬥中哦!別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 誰要陪你們玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼機器人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量接近臨界點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好準備了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速粒子砲命中目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後戰鬥由我們聯合政府處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下可要\N好好的向我說明說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生 您看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量達到臨界值\N合神要被強制解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標靜默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被覆蓋上外骨架般的殼後\N便失去動靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!這算是對待\N總統應有的態度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天\N會重新正式向各位致意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.79,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位也請早一步\N回到自己的崗位比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我話還沒有講完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個機器人\N是在哪裡開發出來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚都集合了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 都已經在官邸集合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.18,0:07:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呀，住手...\N色女，花痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!給我乖一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.85,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要確定您是不是有哪裡不舒服\N不這麼仔細的檢查怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!別這樣!\N不要碰那裡啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有檢查的必要嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各、各位...請不要太過粗暴......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!別這樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是葛萊茵．桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是雷文，是桑德曼先生的副手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛萊茵．桑德曼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊!綾香信上寫的\N城堡的城主就是你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香在哪裡 把姊姊還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封信是我寄給你的\N紅英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為你介紹一下本城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼，剛剛的G戰影\N究竟是誰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等晚點再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.14,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N重要的事情老是都不肯說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G強襲機\N重力子安定指數82%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重鑽機，重粒子中和作業完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量筒不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請從彈藥庫追加補充
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是地球戰騎隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球戰騎隊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由我所創設\N要自外星異種的威脅下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護人類的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要操控這些機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.35,0:09:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體內必須要擁有所謂的\N"G因子"這種特殊的酵素才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?G..什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就想成是\N對於體內的重力異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有的先天性耐力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你\N都是G因子的擁有者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G攻擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們選定你為\N這架戰機的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並為了引誘你主動來到這座城堡\N而假造了這封信，讓你上當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是想讓你搭上攻擊機\N確認一下你適不適合而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.76,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到才正要開始試驗\N外星異種就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.03,0:10:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於用了這麼不完美的方式\N這一點我得向你致歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我想，即使說明了原因\N還是沒辦法得到你的諒解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種智慧超越人類的怪物\N竟然會找上人類下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來，綾香無論什麼事\N都會對我說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能瞞著我\N跑到這種奇怪的地方工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都有表裡兩面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就找綾香出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接問她，就一拍兩瞪眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在訓練中失蹤了\N至今我們都還沒有找到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是很擔心的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種話!我會相信嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種再度開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體進入戰鬥位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會出動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥的話，隨便派個人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.18,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有G因子擁有者的話\N機械是無法正常運轉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你才能駕駛的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要我駕駛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把綾香交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就去駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.23,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他這麼害怕，就饒過他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算少了他一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是可以協助大家\N一起作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是因為害怕才這麼說的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用逞強也沒關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不一樣，你太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖的在這裡等著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說...說我太弱~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個渾蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.62,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確，就算多了個膽小鬼\N也只會礙手礙腳而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的性命已經危在旦夕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是放了那種藉故開溜\N既膽小又沒種的傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就幹給你們看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棺材?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是進入重戰機組的運送櫃\N我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼怪癖好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆，快點坐進去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聒噪了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是個值得鍛鍊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這頭怪物...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次就要你好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安定指數90%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各機組正常運作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距臨界點還有9988點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜，妳是我們女僕的代表\N加油哦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，不要私下交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,型態已經變了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是會進化的機械生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是想到新的作戰方式了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.97,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量、速度跟剛剛都不同嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說牠又進化了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方轉換為遠距離攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣豈不是老挨打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道沒什麼武器嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊機座艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮由我來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要任意行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼口氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力安定指數降至70%以下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急速接近臨界狀態\N這樣很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那招直接攻擊的話\N那就慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有射擊武器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳部武器齊射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 一邊說\N超重火神砲發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊按下右邊紅色按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅..紅色?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器操作系統是採\N語音與按鈕同步進行系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼來著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛彈發射?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!那個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是飛彈，是火神砲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是左邊，是右邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重火神砲發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,定你個頭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這大白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重雷射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重鑽機，超重壓力拳\N準備射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然把拳頭給打出去\N...真是亂搞一通嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子循環達到臨界點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺，請快點呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種，被徹底殲滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.85,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許人類正同時遭到兩大威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我乖一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的檢查才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我好高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意留在城裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是為了你們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到綾香\N我馬上就會閃人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不要脫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.65,0:20:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 連你都不知道\NG戰影的事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰在操控的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.42,0:21:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定有很縝密的心思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只能相信他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又讓妳多了一個難過的經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.85,0:21:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.57,0:21:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.21,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.76,0:22:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.09,0:22:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.47,0:22:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.17,0:22:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.17,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.28,0:22:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.88,0:22:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.52,0:22:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.49,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了!布麗姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺跟英司少爺不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.34,0:22:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?亞孃\N他們倆野到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.61,0:22:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出"迷宮"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週，各位的和平\N也將由我們來照料喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機器人動畫的真．王道傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.56,0:23:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將所有肇始，化作原點\N因而誕生的終極神話，此刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導演:大張正己\N作品:餓狼傳說(TVVlRUS)
